analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Strategic Neutrality Amid Rising Fiscal Volatility. The GMS print of 52 confirms Phase 2 stagnation, where suppressed liquidity convexity and negative market breadth offset localized asset appreciation. While VIX compression suggests near-term stability, the widening of high-yield spreads and the geopolitical shock of global tariffs signal impending regime degradation. Stagnant real interest rates and flat inflation proxies necessitate a disciplined stance, eschewing risk expansion until clarity. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.EN: Strategic Neutrality Amid Rising Fiscal Volatility. While VIX compression suggests near-term stability, the widening of high-yield spreads and the geopolitical shock of global tariffs signal impending regime degradation. reports.ES: Neutralidad estratgica ante la volatilidad fiscal. El GMS de 52 confirma un estancamiento en Fase 2, donde la convexidad de liquidez suprimida y la amplitud negativa del mercado compensan la apreciacin localizada de activos. Aunque la compresin del VIX sugiere estabilidad a corto plazo, el ensanchamiento de los diferenciales de alto rendimiento y los aranceles globales sealan una degradacin del rgimen. Los tipos reales estancados exigen disciplina, evitando el despliegue de capital. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.ID: Netralitas Strategis di Tengah Volatilitas Fiskal. Angka GMS 52 mengonfirmasi stagnasi Fase 2, di mana konveksitas likuiditas yang tertekan dan keluasan pasar negatif mengimbangi apresiasi aset lokal. Meskipun kompresi VIX menunjukkan stabilitas jangka pendek, pelebaran spread imbal hasil tinggi dan guncangan tarif global menandakan degradasi rezim. Suku bunga riil yang stagnan dan proksi inflasi yang datar mengharuskan sikap disiplin, menghindari ekspansi risiko hingga kejelasan tercapai. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.DE: Strategische Neutralitt bei steigender Volatilitt. Der GMS-Wert von 52 besttigt eine Stagnation der Phase 2, in der eine unterdrckte Liquidittskonvexitt und negative Marktbreite die lokale Asset-Appreciation neutralisieren. Whrend die VIX-Kompression kurzfristige Stabilitt suggeriert, signalisieren die Ausweitung der High-Yield-Spreads und geopolitische Zollschocks eine Regime-Degradation. Stagnierende Realzinsen erfordern eine disziplinierte Haltung ohne Risikoexpansion, bis Klarheit herrscht. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.FR: Neutralit stratgique face  la volatilit fiscale. L'indice GMS de 52 confirme une stagnation de phase 2, o la convexit de liquidit supprime et la largeur de march ngative neutralisent l'apprciation locale des actifs. Bien que la compression du VIX suggre une stabilit  court terme, l'largissement des spreads  haut rendement et le choc gopolitique des tarifs mondiaux signalent une dgradation du rgime. Les taux rels stagnants imposent une discipline rigoureuse. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
